TITLE: General Update Pattern in D3.js v4.0
DESCRIPTION: The updated general update pattern for D3.js version 4.0, using the new merge() method to combine enter and update selections after data joining.
SOURCE: https://github.com/d3/d3/blob/main/CHANGES.md#2025-04-11_snippet_49

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
var circle = svg.selectAll("circle").data(data) // UPDATE
    .style("fill", "blue");

circle.exit().remove(); // EXIT

circle.enter().append("circle") // ENTER
    .style("fill", "green")
  .merge(circle) // ENTER + UPDATE
    .style("stroke", "black");
```

