LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const x = d3.scaleUtc([new Date("2000-01-01"), new Date("2000-01-02")], [0, 960]);
x(new Date("2000-01-01T05:00Z")); // 200
x(new Date("2000-01-01T16:00Z")); // 640
x.invert(200); // 2000-01-01T05:00Z
x.invert(640); // 2000-01-01T16:00Z
