DESCRIPTION: Implementation of the Goldstein-Price function, a test function for global optimization used in contour visualization.
SOURCE: https://github.com/d3/d3/blob/main/docs/d3-contour/contour.md#2025-04-11_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
function goldsteinPrice(x, y) {
  return (1 + Math.pow(x + y + 1, 2) * (19 - 14 * x + 3 * x * x - 14 * y + 6 * x * x + 3 * y * y))
      * (30 + Math.pow(2 * x - 3 * y, 2) * (18 - 32 * x + 12 * x * x + 48 * y - 36 * x * y + 27 * y * y));
}
```

